Blobbr,is,a,social,polling,service,that,focuses,on,you,and,your,responses,rather,than,the,aggregate,results,With,Blobbr,you,can,create,and,share,your,position,and,thoughts,with,your,friends,instead,of,just,tallying,up,the,responses,and,lumping,you,in,with,everyone,else,The,Blobbr,API,is,RESTful,with,XML,or,JSON,responses,Some,API,requests,require,authorization,using,your,Blobbr,username,and,password,All,POST,PUT,and,DELETE,requests,require,authorization,and,user,specific,GET,requests,do,as,well